transfer(address,address,uint256,uint256.notice: transfer the required funds plus fees to be sent to the current contract balance

params._amount: is amount to be transfered in kwei
params._destination: is reciever address at the destination rollup
params._feeRampup: will be multiplied by the fee ramp up if the LP claimed and sent the transfer by the startTime block, and will decrease by one for each block after that
params._startTime: is a blocknumber in the future that this transaction can only be executed after

returns._0: the hash of the valid transfer
